, while also providing simple, on-the-fly micro-adjustments. And, they’re white, so you know they’re fast!</p><hr><p><em>This post is sponsored by Specialized and edited by the Bikerumor editorial team. You can check out more of their products at <a href=\"http://www.specialized.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Specialized.com</a>.</em></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"ddf8efb5f74a0f1a74d5775db382323212726e21576c35ab60472da9ee7739cc","category":"Cycling"}